      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely flawless, showroom-quality vehicle! Meticulously maintained and in truly mint condition, it looks and drives exactly like it did the day it was first sold. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine car that has been cared for with the highest level of detail\u2014you won't find a better example on the market!",
