    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for those seeking practical transportation. While the engine and transmission are fully operational and have been maintained, the car does show its age through various cosmetic blemishes, such as minor paint fading and some wear on the interior upholstery. You can expect a reliable ride, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone who prioritizes mechanical functionality over aesthetic perfection.",
