    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in incredible shape\u2014looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every little detail. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. If you're looking for that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis integrity is flawless, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the razor-sharp turn-in these cars are known for. Mechanically synchronized and cosmetically untouched, this M3 represents a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
