    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior finish retains its deep, glass-like factory luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather is supple with zero bolster wear, and every switchgear retains its crisp, tactile feedback. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history and a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as the day it left the assembly line. From the pristine undercarriage to the factory-fresh scent of the interior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example of the model.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
